# BankToSure 🚀

Automated bridge to sync bank transactions into the Sure finance platform.

## 🏦 Supported Banks

| Bank | Status | Provider |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Fortuneo** | ✅ Supported | `FortuneoProvider` |

## 🐳 Docker Mode

**Build:**
```bash
docker build -t banktosure .
```

**Run (Scheduled - 09:00 daily):**
```bash
docker run -d \
  --name banktosure \
  --env-file .env \
  --restart unless-stopped \
  banktosure
```

**Manual Sync (Inside container):**
```bash
docker exec banktosure uv run main.py --days 30
```

## 💻 Local Mode (UV)

**Setup:**
```bash
uv sync
```

**Run Sync:**
```bash
uv run main.py
```

**One-time Historical Import:**
```bash
uv run main.py --days 365
```

**Dry Run:**
```bash
uv run main.py --dry-run
```

## ⚙️ Configuration
Fill your `.env` based on `.env.example`.
- `TZ`: Timezone (default: Europe/Paris)
- `SYNC_TIME`: Schedule time in HH:MM format (default: 09:00)
- `FORTUNEO_ID` / `FORTUNEO_PWD`
- `SURE_API_KEY` / `SURE_ACCOUNT_ID` / `SURE_URL`
- `DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL`
